          "commentary": "8.2 Sam Curran to Ishan, SIX runs. launched again! Full and leg side from Curran. Full pint over midwicket from Kishan. Just a pick-up, lovely hands, pinged off the bat. Flies fully 81 metres into the stands",
          "excitement_score": 5,
          "is_wicket": false,
